ex::newest version 0.02
=======================

An experimental pragma that modifies the behavior of 'use' and 'require'
so that they always load the newest version of modules that have been
installed several times in several places on your system.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires perl 5.7.2 or higher. In fact, it does require an
higher version to work properly with autoloaded and XS modules.

